    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "I see. So when I'm teaching this, is it fair to say that the \"judicial activism\" argument is mostly just a way to undermine established civil rights protections? I want to make sure my students understand if those criticisms are actually based on sound legal theory or if they're just trying to roll back progress.",
